Class DecorationTableConverter

  • java.lang.Object
    • parser.decoration.table.process.DecorationTableConverter
  • public abstract class DecorationTableConverter

    • Method Detail

      • convert

        public static DecorationTableParsingResult convert​(java.io.File jsonFile)
        Transforms decoration table JSON file into POJO before creating a DecorationTableParsingResult. If a parsing error occurs the result will not contain ant DecorationTable. Errors are added to the result. If the error is not a proper parsing error, processing errors can be notified.
        Parameters:
        jsonFile - - path to the seed transducer JSON file representation
        Returns:
        DecorationTableParsingResult containing the DecorationTable result or an empty Optional object and errors if the parsing did't go through

                                                    DecorationTableParsingResult res)
        Process the parsing and converting.
        Parameters:
        pojo - The mapped DecorationTablePOJO related to the Seed Transducer JSON file.
        res - The DecorationTableParsingResult parsing result
        Returns:
        DecorationTableParsingResult containing the DecorationTable result or an empty Optional object and errors if the parsing did't go through
